13
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:47,813
VE-... vos hob ikh gevolt zogn? a! ikh hob gearbet,

14
00:00:48,122 --> 00:00:52,470
ikh bin gegangen nokh milekh. dort iz geven a kleyne TNUVA

15
