vu ikh bin gegangen nokh milekh, un a mentsh hot undz gegebn, ven der S.S. iz aroysgegangen in hoyf...

16
00:01:00,627 --> 00:01:03,980
ULAY MEYUKHAD er iz aroys, shpetsyel...

17
00:01:04,035 --> 00:01:10,450
un, der alter mentsh hot gegebn a bisele milekh trinken far ale BA- BAKHUROT. ze'mir geven fir, finef BAKHUROT,

18
00:01:10,450 --> 00:01:11,808
