19
00:01:11,880 --> 00:01:17,209
 un, keyner hot nisht gevolt antloyfn ven er hot nisht gezen?

20
00:01:16,978 --> 00:01:22,389
LO. iz geven a S.S. mit a biks azoy gegangen hinter undz.

21
00:01:17,670 --> 00:01:19,520
ir hot nisht getrakht...?

22
00:01:22,470 --> 00:01:23,857
⟨K-⟩ KAKHA.

23
00:01:26,108 --> 00:01:30,420
⟨azoy,⟩ azoy gegangen, nisht aleyn gegangen, BETAKH.,

24
