UNK keyner hot nisht gevolt loyfn.

25
00:01:32,638 --> 00:01:36,479
un, vifl shoen hot men gearbet a tog?

26
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:40,230
 ⟨nu, a⟩ finef, zeks sho.

27
00:01:40,755 --> 00:01:43,651
gearbet? nor finef, zeks sho?

28
00:01:41,498 --> 00:01:43,618
yo. yo.

29
00:01:43,962 --> 00:01:51,718
mitog, m'iz arayngekumen. m'hot gegesn mitog, vos m'hot shoyn gekokht, kartofl mit di sholekhts mit a bisele MARAK.

30
00:01:52,315 --> 00:01:58,147
un nokh mitog, un m'hot gemakht a bisl NOAKH, ⟨un⟩ nokh mitog, m'hot zikh genemen...

31
00:01:58,643 --> 00:02:00,122
