42
00:02:34,620 --> 00:02:43,920
⟨nu,⟩ zog ikh, bay di blokn iz geven azoy gemakht glaykh, azoy vi di PAROT zenen geshlofn, eyner, vi hering, eyner lebn di andere, zekhtsik mentshn,

43
00:02:43,920 --> 00:02:45,262
zekhtsik froyen.

44
00:02:45,061 --> 00:02:46,061
un...

45
00:02:45,808 --> 00:02:48,226
mener iz geven a andere lager,

46
00:02:48,226 --> 00:02:51,995
lebn, opgeteylt: di froyen-lager mit,

47
00:02:52,221 --> 00:02:57,851
mit a ployt. EKH OM-...? GEDER iz geven opgeteylt di froyen-lager, un ekstre di mener-lager.

48
00:02:59,190 --> 00:03:01,300
yo. ⟨un⟩...

49
00:03:00,135 --> 00:03:04,668
un, ir hot gede- i- ir hot gehat mit vos tsu dekn zikh?

50
00:03:04,590 --> 00:03:05,934
