vayl ⟨es iz⟩ geven, ven m'iz gekumen in lager, m'hot tsugenemen di zakhn.

53
00:03:16,352 --> 00:03:18,374
m'hot getrogn di gantse derekh

54
00:03:18,374 --> 00:03:20,868
a rukzak, a... vi azoy zogt men BEIVRIT?

55
00:03:20,509 --> 00:03:21,509
SAK.

56
00:03:21,111 --> 00:03:22,809
a SAK, a rukzak,

57
00:03:23,119 --> 00:03:31,882
un m'iz gekumen in di ershte lager, Landsberg, m'hot dos ales avekgenemen. di S.S.kes, far a, a por mentshn, froyen, ⟨hobn⟩ gegebn tsurik di mantl.

58
00:03:31,882 --> 00:03:34,099
eyn kleyd iz geblibn oyf undz.

59
00:03:34,695 --> 00:03:37,750
eyn kleyd! nu?

60
00:03:38,931 --> 00:03:43,281
un, ober in TÜRKHEIM hot men undz gegebn hoyzn.

61
00:03:43,281 --> 00:03:49,522
di la- di, dort iz geven mener, un m'hot tsugenemen fun di mener di hoyzn, lange;

62
00:03:49,579 --> 00:03:51,615
m'hot undz gegebn dos,

63
00:03:51,857 --> 00:03:53,032
far di froyen.

64
00:03:53,562 --> 00:03:55,429
iz, yo.

65
00:03:55,688 --> 00:03:57,082
azoy iz geven.

66
00:03:57,230 --> 00:03:58,230
un...

67
00:03:57,257 --> 00:03:59,715
m'hot tsugenemen di zakhn, un m'hot geshlofn mi-

68
00:03:59,772 --> 00:04:07,616
mit eyn, ikh hob geshlofn mit di... ober s'iz geven froyen vos m'hot zey tsugenemen di mantlen oykhet. ikh veys vi azoy zey hobn geshlo- ober BASOF,

69
