77
00:04:42,769 --> 00:04:45,378
ikh a bisele getrunken fun di top,

78
00:04:45,452 --> 00:04:47,032
un a bisele di

79
00:04:47,157 --> 00:04:48,453
andere froy.

80
00:04:48,453 --> 00:04:51,487
eyn top ho'mir gekrign vegn tsvey mentshn.

81
00:04:50,470 --> 00:04:52,432
f- far tsvey mentshn?

82
00:04:51,949 --> 00:04:54,140
yo, ho'mir getrunken fun eyn top.

83
00:04:53,590 --> 00:04:57,377
 un vos hot men geredt tsvishn di froyen?

84
00:04:57,467 --> 00:04:58,575
vos hot men...?

85
00:04:57,930 --> 00:05:00,651
