un vos hot men, ⟨⟩... yo?

97
00:05:48,131 --> 00:05:52,541
ir hot gekent klern oyf epes? dermanen zikh dortn?

98
00:05:50,742 --> 00:05:57,148
LO! gorn- dort hot men nisht gekent lernen gornisht. m'hot geredt oyf di tsores: v⟨i⟩ m'iz arayngefaln,

99
