iz geven, tifus.

104
00:06:19,299 --> 00:06:20,455
du veyst vos...?

105
00:06:20,455 --> 00:06:22,809
flektifus. d⟨i zenen⟩ geshtorbn, yo,

106
00:06:22,809 --> 00:06:25,239
fun ander lager, vos ⟨zenen⟩ gekumen bay undz.

107
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,120
⟨⟩.

108
00:06:25,239 --> 00:06:27,996
LO, bay undz iz geven reyn. s'iz geven a,

109
00:06:28,322 --> 00:06:33,952
a froy fun Budapest. zi hot gemakht⟨, ah,⟩ vesh. a vesheray iz geven

110
00:06:34,043 --> 00:06:36,056
un zi hot gevashn di vesh.

111
00:06:36,056 --> 00:06:38,790
itst nokh vel ikh zogn: zi hot geshvangert.

112
