127
00:07:29,815 --> 00:07:37,673
ver s'iz geven krank? nu, iz geven aza kleyne... "REVIER" hot dos geheysn, aza kleyne, KEILU, azoy vi a BET KHOLIM.

128
00:07:37,864 --> 00:07:40,288
