129
00:07:40,935 --> 00:07:43,932
un m'hot im epes gegebn, a refues?

130
00:07:44,277 --> 00:07:47,277
ULAY yo. ikh gedenk, s'iz geven epes a dokter.

131
00:07:47,277 --> 00:07:52,339
a tseyn-dokter, gedenk ikh, iz geven, ober azoy, andere dokter, veys ikh, gedenk ikh nisht,

132
