nor ULAY m'hot gegebn epes. ober geshtorbn iz nisht keyner. keyner.

133
00:07:57,895 --> 00:08:01,669
un, m'hot gekent aroysgeyn fun TÜRKHEIM?

134
00:08:01,489 --> 00:08:04,200
LO!, LO, LO.

135
00:08:03,868 --> 00:08:04,554
⟨KEN⟩.

136
00:08:04,476 --> 00:08:11,332
aroysgeyn hot gekent, s'iz geven BAKHURIM fun, Grikhnland, iz geven, YEHUDIM,

137
00:08:11,332 --> 00:08:15,708
nor zey ⟨hot, hobn⟩ gekent geyn fray. ikh veys nisht far vos zey hobn gekent geyn fray.

138
00:08:16,002 --> 00:08:18,881
zey zenen geven kapos. host gehert fun kapo?

139
00:08:18,938 --> 00:08:28,972
zey zenen geven kapos, di, fun Grikhnland, di BAKHURIM, un zey hobn gekent geyn in TÜRKHEIM, zenen gekumen tsurik. zey zenen gegangen un gekumen tsurik, ober nisht avekgelofn.

140
00:08:29,451 --> 00:08:32,128
LO, LO, zenen gekumen, BETAKH.

141
00:08:34,092 --> 00:08:35,436
un,...

142
00:08:35,813 --> 00:08:41,460
