143
00:08:42,765 --> 00:08:46,134
azoy, ⟨di⟩ GERMANIM ven m'iz gegangen mit di AGALA,

144
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:52,212
zog ikh, hot men geholfn. di, der mentsh vos hot gegebn milekh un, azoy a

145
00:08:52,212 --> 00:08:59,246
shtikele kez a vorf getun. ikh hob gehat a groyse tash in mayne mantl; azoy iz geneyt geven, a,

146
