a KIS geneyt, un dort hob ikh arayngeleygt,

147
00:09:02,712 --> 00:09:06,586
un ven m'iz gekumen BIFNIM BElager, BEMAKHANE,

148
00:09:06,593 --> 00:09:09,135
ho'mir zikh tseteylt di por...

149
00:09:09,259 --> 00:09:15,615
nor mir hobn geredt az s'iz nokh do gute GE- GERMANIM oykhet, az zey helfn a bisele di YEHUDIM.

150
00:09:15,739 --> 00:09:17,370
un,

151
00:09:17,697 --> 00:09:21,808
