yo, a SMIKHA.

153
00:09:22,928 --> 00:09:24,694
ven iz dos gevezn?

154
00:09:24,784 --> 00:09:27,194
dos iz geven azoy BEEMTSA,

155
00:09:27,194 --> 00:09:31,831
nisht in gantsn BESOF, BEEMTSA, geshikt⟨,⟩ kilo tsuker...

156
00:09:31,888 --> 00:09:36,585
oykh di goy fun, vos er hot gearbet in kikh, der MENAHEL,

157
00:09:36,585 --> 00:09:39,071
er hot oykh gekrign aza KHAVILA...

158
00:09:39,178 --> 00:09:41,517
kilo tsuker mit a SMIKHA.

159
00:09:41,912 --> 00:09:47,860
oykh geven gut. ver hot nisht gehat a mantl, iz geven gut az zey hobn gekrign a SMIKHA tsudekn.

160
00:09:49,118 --> 00:09:52,236
un, oyf shtroy iz men geshlofn,

161
00:09:52,236 --> 00:10:00,384
azoy vi di PAROT shlofn oyf ⟨K-⟩ shtroy. oyf di gantse leng iz geven nor shtroy. in shtroy iz oykh geven KINIM. m'hot zikh gekent makhn reyn...

162
00:10:00,593 --> 00:10:03,062
ven ikh makh haynt aza kalte tush,

163
00:10:03,062 --> 00:10:05,497
ikh hob eyn un fertsik grad fiber.

164
00:10:05,554 --> 00:10:11,820
ikh hob gemakht in di greste, KHOREF iz geven, shtark kalt BEGERMANYA.

165
00:10:12,034 --> 00:10:18,322
un, m'hot gedarft tushn mit kalte vaser, vashn di ho- kop mit kalt vaser, tushn mit kalt vaser.

166
00:10:18,514 --> 00:10:25,660
nisht geholfn gornisht: AFILU gevashn, ober in di shtroy vos m'iz geshlofn iz shoyn geven ful KINIM dortn, onge-...

167
00:10:25,669 --> 00:10:27,755
un azoy hot men gelebt.

168
00:10:29,854 --> 00:10:33,088
dos vet zayn a gedenk-tseykhn oyf di gantse lebn.

169
00:10:35,119 --> 00:10:39,770
un vos, ir gedenkt nokh epes az ir vilt dertseyln fun TÜRKHEIM?

170
