UNK nisht gornisht.

176
00:11:05,882 --> 00:11:10,980
gornisht. vos hot, s'hot pasirt, s'hot genug pasirt, vos s'hot pasirt.

177
00:11:11,417 --> 00:11:15,393
yo, ober yeder hot zayne privat...

178
00:11:15,585 --> 00:11:17,756
private zakhn? UNK

179
00:11:16,800 --> 00:11:17,756
yo.

180
00:11:18,488 --> 00:11:22,280
s'iz geven dortn meydelekh, ⟨v-⟩

181
