vos mit di grikhishe BAKHURIM ⟨hobn⟩ gemakht a lebn,

182
00:11:25,682 --> 00:11:30,885
⟨lebn,⟩, ge- far a tsigaret ⟨zenen zey⟩ gegangen shlofn mit zey. dos ikh veys.

183
00:11:30,992 --> 00:11:33,905
nor nisht ale meydelekh geven azoy,

184
00:11:34,165 --> 00:11:36,926
vegn a tsigaret geyn un lign mit di...

185
00:11:37,337 --> 00:11:44,874
zey hobn gehat ekstre BLOKIM, ekstre TSRIFIM, di grikhishe BAKHURIM vos zenen geven kapos,

186
00:11:45,353 --> 00:11:50,882
un zey hobn shoyn getrofn meydelekh azelekhe. vegn tsigaretn hobn zey gegangen mit zey

187
00:11:51,040 --> 00:11:52,215
makhn a lebn.

188
00:11:53,048 --> 00:11:56,580
dos ikh veys. kh'hob nisht gehaltn di lekht far zey,

189
00:11:56,580 --> 00:11:59,380
ober ikh hob gehert vos

190
00:11:59,427 --> 00:12:00,906
dortn tut zikh.

191
00:12:02,633 --> 00:12:03,606
KEN.

192
00:12:04,776 --> 00:12:07,360
 un di DEUTSCHE hobn gornisht gezogt?

193
00:12:08,168 --> 00:12:09,799
zey hobn nisht gevust?

194
00:12:08,488 --> 00:12:11,502
nu, zey hobn zikh gehit fun di DEUTSCHn.

195
00:12:11,644 --> 00:12:13,420
zey hobn zikh gehit.

196
00:12:13,450 --> 00:12:15,870
⟨ikh meyn az⟩ nisht.

197
00:12:16,420 --> 00:12:24,457
eyn mol, ikh gedenk, iz ave-... dortn m'hot getseylt BABOKER di mentshn, un oyf der nakht ven m'iz arayngekumen.

198
00:12:24,457 --> 00:12:28,980
PITOM, m'hot gezogt, m'hot gezogt az se felt a meydl.

199
00:12:30,797 --> 00:12:33,187
ULAY fun di SADE...

200
00:12:33,278 --> 00:12:36,090
m'hot gearbet in droysn oyf di SADE, zogt men?

201
00:12:37,193 --> 00:12:40,790
 ULAY dort epes a GERMANI hot zi avekgekhapt

202
00:12:41,125 --> 00:12:44,764
⟨z-⟩ bay zikh in TÜRKHEIM, in di dorf, ⟨u⟩n,...

203
00:12:45,107 --> 00:12:50,281
⟨un m'- zenen dernokh⟩ di GERMANIM, m'hot getseylt un getseylt un m'hot gezogt, tomer

204
00:12:51,385 --> 00:12:59,510
az m'vet zi trefn, me hengt zi oyf, LITLOT. me vet zi... ober m'hot zi nisht getrofn, un m'hot nisht gemakht LITLOT keynem, ⟨un⟩...

205
00:12:59,510 --> 00:13:02,871
⟨ober⟩ zi hot men gevolt makhn LITLOT, vos zi iz avekgelofn.

206
00:13:03,332 --> 00:13:07,218
ober ikh, m'hot gemeynt az epes a GERMANI iz gekumen dortn

207
00:13:07,218 --> 00:13:10,020
bay di SADE, bay di feld,

208
00:13:10,082 --> 00:13:15,071
un hot zi a khap gegebn. m'hot zi gevolt rateven ULAY, ikh veys,

209
00:13:15,094 --> 00:13:16,387
avekgekh-...

210
00:13:15,460 --> 00:13:17,568
un zi hot nisht tsurikgekumen?

211
00:13:16,748 --> 00:13:21,680
LO. m'hot getseyl⟨t⟩ hundert mol, nisht eyn mol, un m'hot nisht getrofn.

212
00:13:20,173 --> 00:13:22,680
 un vos hot men gemakht?

213
00:13:21,895 --> 00:13:29,660
gornisht. m'hot keynem nisht oyfgehongen. zi hot men gevolt oyfhengen, tomer m'vet zi trefn. m'hot gevust di nomen ire, ver se felt,

214
00:13:29,826 --> 00:13:34,882
ober keyner, s'iz gornisht gevorn, m'hot keynem nisht oyfgehongen VEZEHU.

215
00:13:35,260 --> 00:13:37,431
un zi, ULAY, ⟨hot,⟩

216
00:13:37,926 --> 00:13:42,175
gehat MAZAL: m'iz gekumen, emetser, geholfn, zi avekgenemen

217
00:13:42,175 --> 00:13:43,488
in di dorf.

218
00:13:42,853 --> 00:13:46,458
un ir gedenk- er iz gevezn nokh a mol aza...?

219
00:13:46,043 --> 00:13:48,247
neyn, neyn. eyn mol iz geven dos.

220
00:13:48,166 --> 00:13:49,833
vos m'hot antlofn.

221
00:13:48,540 --> 00:13:49,597
eyn mol.

222
00:13:49,637 --> 00:13:52,340
m'hot gearbet bay di SADE oykhet.

223
00:13:52,506 --> 00:13:54,542
m'hot gekloybt, ikh veys,

224
00:13:54,885 --> 00:13:59,654
vos me leygt oyf di fayer, azelekhe kleyne... dos hot men gekloybt bay di SADE.

225
00:13:59,998 --> 00:14:03,700
eyn mol iz geven Mengel- Mengele oykhet.

226
00:14:03,643 --> 00:14:04,447
yo?

227
00:14:03,700 --> 00:14:05,966
eyn mol mit a mototsik, yo.

228
00:14:06,259 --> 00:14:08,840
er iz gekumen mit a mototsik.

229
00:14:08,554 --> 00:14:10,708
un vos ⟨f⟩⟨UNK⟩...?

230
00:14:09,465 --> 00:14:17,289
un m'iz gegangen, m'hot undz geshikt arbetn bay di SADE kloybn groz. s'iz shoyn geven BASOF; s'iz shoyn nisht geven azoy OKHEL,

231
00:14:17,312 --> 00:14:20,464
hot men dos gekokht, di YEREK fun di feld.

232
00:14:20,464 --> 00:14:26,800
hot men dos gekokht un dos hot men gegebn esn. UNK ikh gedenk, in yenem tog iz men gegangen kloybn di YEREK,

233
00:14:27,184 --> 00:14:28,578
vegn ts⟨u⟩ kokhn.

234
00:14:28,973 --> 00:14:31,414
geven a hoykher BAKHUR.

235
00:14:31,572 --> 00:14:34,810
er hot geredt oykh HUNGARIT, Mengele.

236
00:14:35,115 --> 00:14:43,212
ikh hob nisht gehert, nor me- andere mentshn vos zey hobn ⟨im⟩ gekent fun AUSCHWITZ, m'hot im gezen, gekent, az er iz a HUNGARI geven,

237
00:14:43,212 --> 00:14:44,526
geredt HUNGARIT.

238
00:14:43,215 --> 00:14:46,650
, un far vos hot er gekumen?

239
00:14:46,675 --> 00:14:49,993
dos ikh veys nisht. redn mit a daytsh dortn, mit di

240
00:14:47,299 --> 00:14:48,322
aha.

241
00:14:50,067 --> 00:14:53,000
greste daytsh fun di lager.

242
00:14:53,188 --> 00:14:54,532
geven di...

243
00:14:55,180 --> 00:14:59,122
s'iz geven a daytsh vos er iz geven der MENAHEL der grester.

244
00:14:59,449 --> 00:15:02,400
iz mit im UNK. m'hot gezen az me redt.

245
00:15:02,503 --> 00:15:04,032
ven undz ze'mir gegangen

246
00:15:04,073 --> 00:15:09,146
BESHURA, bay di SADE, ho'mir gezen az er redt mit dem andern S.S.

247
00:15:09,574 --> 00:15:13,213
s'iz gekumen a sakh mol S.S.n dortn. ikh veys vosere

248
00:15:13,303 --> 00:15:15,423
kontrol zey hobn gemakht dortn.

249
00:15:17,674 --> 00:15:19,473
m'hot gemakht kontroln.

250
00:15:20,577 --> 00:15:24,469
nor ver iz geblibn lebn, dos iz a groyse nes.

251
00:15:25,285 --> 00:15:28,131
BEEMET a groyse nes fun di...

252
00:15:30,448 --> 00:15:33,783
un, ir gedenkt der bafrayer-tog,

253
00:15:33,874 --> 00:15:36,100
ven m'hot aykh bafrayert?

254
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:37,091
yo.

255
00:15:36,456 --> 00:15:38,056
vos gedenkt ir

256
00:15:38,056 --> 00:15:39,251
fun dem tog?

257
00:15:39,527 --> 00:15:41,765
der S.S. UNK,

258
00:15:41,839 --> 00:15:45,916
vos ikh zog, der groyser S.S. vos hot geredt mit Mengelen, hot,

259
00:15:46,446 --> 00:15:48,465
a vayse fon geleygt

260
00:15:49,737 --> 00:15:51,990
bay di lager-hoyf

261
00:15:52,099 --> 00:15:58,520
un geredt. UNK ikh gedenk shoyn nisht vos er hot geredt BEEMET. er hot geredt un,...

262
00:15:57,921 --> 00:15:59,280
un dernokh?

263
00:15:59,575 --> 00:16:07,584
nu, nokh dem, yeder eyner, vu hot er gevoynt, vu hot ge- eynem, a sakh BAKHUROT zenen geblibn voynen in, in lager,

264
00:16:03,560 --> 00:16:04,960
⟨n-...⟩

265
00:16:07,303 --> 00:16:08,140
yo.

266
00:16:07,827 --> 00:16:08,946
in MAKHANE,

267
00:16:08,946 --> 00:16:12,596
un a sakh zenen gegangen in di, TÜRKHEIM iz a kleyne

268
00:16:12,602 --> 00:16:16,110
KFAR. a KFAR, nisht a IR, TÜRKHEIM.

269
00:16:16,110 --> 00:16:22,870
un yeder eyner hot zikh gezukht bayn a... ikh hob gezukht, ikh hob getrofn dort vu, milekh hot er geteylt.

270
00:16:22,870 --> 00:16:24,590
ikh hob gevoynt bay im.

271
00:16:24,590 --> 00:16:28,678
andere BAKHUROT hobn gevoynt in andere ple- oykh bay GERMANIM.

272
00:16:28,954 --> 00:16:31,276
m'hot gevoynt bay di GERMANIM, KEN.

273
00:16:30,287 --> 00:16:33,757
 BUT, ver hot aykh bafrayt?

274
00:16:34,320 --> 00:16:37,300
di AMERIKANIM, AMERIKAIM.

275
00:16:35,873 --> 00:16:36,997
yo.

276
00:16:37,240 --> 00:16:40,960
zey hobn arayngekumen UNK zey hobn epes gezogt?

277
00:16:41,323 --> 00:16:46,910
 m'hot..., nisht koydem, nisht di AMERIKAIM. koydem iz gekumen Frankraykh,

278
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:51,527
KUSHIM iz geven dortn, un nokh dem amerikanishe soldatn.

279
00:16:52,326 --> 00:16:59,655
a amerikanishe soldat hot geharget a... a yidishe, s'iz geven yidishe soldatn amerikanishe...⟨er⟩ hot geharget...

280
00:16:59,655 --> 00:17:02,057
nisht BEKAVANA, BLI KAVANA...

281
00:17:03,008 --> 00:17:06,530
er hot, geputst di ROVE,

282
00:17:06,602 --> 00:17:10,038
un s'iz aroysgegangen oyf a yidishe meydl di koyl,

283
00:17:10,263 --> 00:17:12,944
un gevorn geharget. iz geven a LEVAYA.

284
00:17:12,944 --> 00:17:15,650
m'hot zi geleygt lebn,

285
00:17:16,520 --> 00:17:20,780
, zeks,... nu,

286
00:17:20,780 --> 00:17:27,081
TAYASIM toyte, vos fun di MILKHAMA iz geven zeks TAYASIM dort in GERMANYA, in TÜRKHEIM, bay di heylike ort.

287
00:17:27,375 --> 00:17:29,191
iz geven,

288
00:17:30,261 --> 00:17:32,550
zeks TAYASIM un far ir.

289
00:17:32,607 --> 00:17:35,402
zi iz oykh dortn, m'hot zi geleygt dortn,

290
00:17:35,458 --> 00:17:37,261
l⟨eg-⟩ lign lebn zey.

291
00:17:37,261 --> 00:17:39,970
ikh bin oykh geven bay di LEVAYA, MISKENA.

292
00:17:39,970 --> 00:17:42,016
a sheyn meydele, a yung meydele,

293
00:17:42,951 --> 00:17:45,729
fun zibetsn, akhtsn yor.

294
00:17:46,562 --> 00:17:51,551
UNK ⟨d-⟩ er hot nisht gevolt; er iz geven oykhet a... s'iz geven a sakh,

295
00:17:52,485 --> 00:17:56,900
amerikanishe soldatn iz geven, KHAYALIM AMERIKAIM,

296
00:17:56,900 --> 00:17:58,287
UNK zey zenen

297
00:17:58,287 --> 00:18:00,107
gekumen oykhet dortn,

298
00:18:01,041 --> 00:18:03,590
⟨un zey hobn⟩ geshosn.

299
00:18:02,042 --> 00:18:06,200
un ir, ⟨u-⟩ un m'hot aykh bafrayt, un ir, ir hot gev- ⟨i-⟩

300
00:18:06,200 --> 00:18:10,384
ir gezunt, gevezn gezunt, ir hot gekent geyn tsum TÜRKHEIM?

301
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:13,437
yo, ikh hob gekent geyn, KEN.

302
00:18:10,828 --> 00:18:11,902
yo?

303
00:18:13,579 --> 00:18:19,890
un ir hot gegangen tsun, tsu der, familye, yo? yo. ⟨i⟩n...

304
00:18:16,768 --> 00:18:19,479
voynen, yo, bay dem altn mentsh.

305
00:18:19,553 --> 00:18:27,530
ober nisht a sakh tsayt ze'mir gezesn dortn. nokh dem hot men gezogt, s'iz do a transport TSHEKHI. s'iz geven ungarishe transport,

306
00:18:27,530 --> 00:18:32,113
nor ikh hob nisht gevolt, blaybn dortn, un nokh dem aleyn ikh'l darfn forn.

307
00:18:32,113 --> 00:18:36,160
ikh hob nisht gevolt forn mit di ungarishe transport.

308
00:18:36,259 --> 00:18:40,660
ikh hob gehert az di tshekhishe transport nemt men,

309
00:18:41,035 --> 00:18:44,488
un bin ikh oykh gegangen. m'hot undz gefirt.

310
00:18:44,578 --> 00:18:46,833
un vu, vu hot ir geforn?

311
00:18:47,076 --> 00:18:49,264
m'hot undz gefirt in MÜNCHEN,

312
00:18:49,489 --> 00:18:54,820
un ikh gedenk nisht nokh vu. m'hot undz shoyn, gefirt oyf aheym, oyf aheym,

313
00:18:54,636 --> 00:18:57,650
un vu hot ir, un vu zent ir geforn?

314
00:18:55,024 --> 00:18:56,700
oyf TSHEKHYA.

315
00:18:58,315 --> 00:19:06,004
zog ikh, oyf,... a! koydem bin ikh geforn in Budapest. ikh bin geblibn shteyn in Budapest. ikh bin arayn bay mayne BOSIT,

316
00:19:06,280 --> 00:19:15,302
un zi hot gevolt, zol ikh teykef kumen arbetn, ober ikh hob gezogt, "ikh vil geyn zen MISHPAKHA. ULAY UNK geblibn lebn. ikh muz geyn zen

317
00:19:15,477 --> 00:19:17,158
ver iz geblibn lebn."

318
00:19:17,265 --> 00:19:23,519
hot zi gezogt, "BESEDER." zi iz farshtanen; zi iz oykh geven in lager, zi iz oykh geven a YEHUDIYA.

319
00:19:23,965 --> 00:19:31,181
iz hot zi gezogt, "kum tsurik. gey, zits a bisl, a por vokhn BABAYIT, un dernokh dem, kum tsurik." un azoy iz geven.

320
00:19:31,845 --> 00:19:42,453
ven ikh bin shoyn avekgeforn fun di shtot MUKAČEVO, nokh tsvey vokhn, di RUSIM, RUSYA hot tsugemakht di GVUL. ven ikh zits nokh tsvey vokhn, ikh ken nisht aroysgeyn,

321
00:19:41,840 --> 00:19:43,540
 aha.

322
00:19:42,493 --> 00:19:47,448
darf ikh blaybn dortn, o, a sakh yorn biz ven me lozt aroys.

323
00:19:47,455 --> 00:19:53,210
un, ir hot geforn nokh MUKAČEV, un vi lang zent ir dort gevezn?

324
00:19:52,534 --> 00:19:54,131
a por vokhn.

325
00:19:53,762 --> 00:19:55,042
 un...

326
00:19:54,137 --> 00:19:57,303
⟨dernokh⟩ bin ikh geforn tsurik arbetn dortn bay mayn...

327
00:19:55,183 --> 00:19:56,116
yo.

328
00:19:56,116 --> 00:19:59,970
yo, un ir kumt tsu MUKAČEV, un vemen hot ir getrofn?

329
00:19:59,588 --> 00:20:02,299
nu, hob ikh getrofn mayn groyse bruder.

330
00:20:02,642 --> 00:20:09,521
mayn groyse bruder. un di kleyne bruder iz gekumen oykh fun di MA- fun di lagern. er iz geven in AUSCHWITZ,

331
00:20:09,595 --> 00:20:11,743
un nokh in andere lagern.

332
00:20:11,743 --> 00:20:16,780
di groyse iz geven nor, m'hot im genemen, di HUNGARIM hobn im genemen oyf arbet nor,

333
00:20:16,780 --> 00:20:18,887
nisht in a MAKHANE, lager.

334
00:20:19,332 --> 00:20:20,636
ikh bin nokh ge-

335
00:20:20,636 --> 00:20:27,968
kh'hob nisht gevust vu er voynt afile. kh'hob gefregt dort fun mentshn, fun yidn, vu may- azoy un azoy, di nomen, Lakhmanovitsh,

336
00:20:27,968 --> 00:20:30,300
vu voynt? hot men mir gezogt.

337
00:20:30,537 --> 00:20:33,478
azoy hob ikh getrofn mayn bruder, un

338
00:20:33,478 --> 00:20:35,222
geven a por vokhn.

339
00:20:35,329 --> 00:20:41,212
un, un, ir hot gegangen aheym ts- ir hot gezukht ayer heym? un v- ver hot...?

340
00:20:39,092 --> 00:20:41,566
yo, BETAKH. keyner,

341
00:20:41,691 --> 00:20:46,157
keyner. di gantse gas iz geven leydik, nisht geven keyn mentshn shoyn,

342
00:20:46,517 --> 00:20:48,418
un ver hot dort gevoynt?

343
00:20:46,737 --> 00:20:48,081
ales a-...

344
00:20:48,357 --> 00:20:49,450
keyner!

345
00:20:49,450 --> 00:20:56,270
mayne mame, A-, IMA mitn ABA, keyner, di gantse gas iz geven leydik,

346
00:20:56,270 --> 00:21:00,956
ales aroysgeganvet. ikh veys nisht ver hot avekgenemen di meblen mit di zakhn,

347
00:21:01,367 --> 00:21:02,710
ULAY ⟨d-⟩...

348
00:21:01,603 --> 00:21:03,841
ir hot gornisht getrofn?

349
00:21:02,710 --> 00:21:04,466
gornisht, gornisht.

350
00:21:04,101 --> 00:21:06,221
nor ayere tsvey brider?

351
00:21:05,721 --> 00:21:10,696
nor di... neyn! koydem ⟨di,⟩ eyn bruder, vemen kh'hob gezukht vu er voynt.

352
00:21:09,518 --> 00:21:11,756
 yo.

353
00:21:10,696 --> 00:21:13,105
di andere iz gekumen oykhet

354
00:21:13,433 --> 00:21:16,000
fun di MAKHANE. ⟨KEN⟩.

355
00:21:13,500 --> 00:21:18,337
 ven ir zent dort gevezn?.

356
00:21:16,285 --> 00:21:20,379
yo, iz er oykhet aheymgekumen, ho'mir zikh ale dortn getrofn.

357
00:21:20,419 --> 00:21:23,805
oykh mayne shvegerin's shvester zenen gekumen.

358
00:21:23,895 --> 00:21:25,846
mayn bruder's froy...

359
00:21:25,887 --> 00:21:30,218
a! di bruder's froy iz oykh geblibn lebn. zi iz geven in a lager, in AUSCHWITZ.

360
00:21:30,325 --> 00:21:36,174
zi iz gekumen oykh aheym, ⟨azoy vos, ven,⟩ zi iz geven, d- geven di KHATUNA ven mayn IMA hot nokh gelebt,

361
00:21:36,822 --> 00:21:44,280
ober zey zenen gek- er iz gekumen aheym fun di arbet vu m'hot im genemen, un zi iz gekumen fun AUSCHWITZ a-...

362
00:21:44,280 --> 00:21:46,440
yo. zey hobn zikh getrofn tsurik.

363
00:21:46,879 --> 00:21:50,610
zenen, zi iz oykh geven do. zi iz do geshtorbn; zi iz geven krank.

364
00:21:52,093 --> 00:21:53,369
un ZEHU.

365
00:21:53,325 --> 00:22:02,130
 un, ir hot ⟨g-⟩ andere mentshn hot ir, getrofn in MUKAČEV, UNK

366
00:22:01,881 --> 00:22:09,519
 kh'hob getrofn di MORE, di MORE vos ikh bin gegangen in shule UKRAINIT, hob ikh getrofn, geredt mit i-...

367
00:22:02,674 --> 00:22:04,560
fun shul, fun...?

368
00:22:08,447 --> 00:22:10,346
nu, er hot zikh ba- gefreyt?

369
00:22:10,386 --> 00:22:11,544
ver, er?

370
00:22:11,112 --> 00:22:14,660
yo. ⟨er⟩ iz geven...? yo?.

371
00:22:12,073 --> 00:22:14,466
yo, yo, er hot zikh gefreyt, KEN.

372
00:22:14,466 --> 00:22:17,450
kh'hob nokh gekent demls UKRAINIT redn. yetst ikh

373
00:22:17,473 --> 00:22:21,112
ken nisht mer azoy., finef, tsvey, dray verter ikh ken nokh.

374
00:22:21,658 --> 00:22:24,321
un vemen nokh? neyn, azoy nisht,

375
00:22:24,321 --> 00:22:27,550
nor di MORE UK- fun UKRAINIT.

376
00:22:27,050 --> 00:22:31,220
un vi hot ir ge- gesh- geshpirt kumen tsurik in...

377
00:22:31,446 --> 00:22:33,380
vi hot men zikh geshpirt?

378
00:22:33,910 --> 00:22:36,519
vi azoy m'hot zikh gefilt az m'iz gekumen tsurik?

379
00:22:35,057 --> 00:22:36,519
yo.

380
00:22:37,605 --> 00:22:47,842
nu, ⟨me⟩, m'hot zikh nisht gefilt gut. az m'iz gegangen bay di shtub fun di HORIM un m'hot nisht getrofn keynem, hot men nisht gefilt gut, oder vos hot men gekent makhn?

381
00:22:48,507 --> 00:22:53,513
UNK gegangen bodn. dort iz ge- ikh ken gut shvimen; ikh bin gegangen shvimen.

382
00:22:53,822 --> 00:22:58,476
un mayn shvegerin iz geven a shnayderin. ikh hob ir geholfn a bisele neyen,

383
00:22:58,476 --> 00:23:03,232
un bay di shtub, ikh hob ir geholfn, di parketn gemakht, reyn,

384
00:23:03,340 --> 00:23:11,060
KVISA ikh hob ir gemakht. kh'hob ge- farnemen zikh a bisele, fargesn fun di TSAROT. KEN.

385
00:23:09,938 --> 00:23:17,256
un, far vos zent ir tsurikgegangen tsum, ⟨n-⟩ nokh Budapest, un nisht geblaybt in MUKAČEV?

386
00:23:18,578 --> 00:23:20,344
far vos?

387
00:23:21,683 --> 00:23:26,233
ikh hob tsugezogt far mayne mayster, far di BOSIT, az ikh kum tsurik.

388
00:23:27,100 --> 00:23:33,543
ikh hob ir, zi hot gebetn et- tsen mol, zol ikh kumen, zol ikh kumen tsurik. nu, ikh hob ir gezogt, "ikh

389
00:23:28,905 --> 00:23:30,110
un s'-...

390
00:23:31,774 --> 00:23:33,742
 un s'iz aykh gut geven?

391
00:23:33,543 --> 00:23:35,312
zog dir tsu, ikh kum."

392
00:23:35,132 --> 00:23:37,843
s'iz aykh gut gevezn in Budapest?

393
00:23:37,427 --> 00:23:38,518
far mir?

394
00:23:38,338 --> 00:23:40,711
mit ir tsu arbetn dort?

395
00:23:39,655 --> 00:23:43,052
yo, yo. zi iz geven zeyer a NEKHMADA BAKHURA,

396
00:23:43,052 --> 00:23:46,247
⟨KAKHA⟩ UNK ESRIM VESHESH, nisht a yunge BAKHURA,

397
00:23:46,270 --> 00:23:50,747
ober zi hot nokh dem geheyratet. zi hot getrofn a BAKHUR un zi hot geheyratet.

398
00:23:50,747 --> 00:23:54,270
nor ikh bin avekgeforn; ikh hobn shoyn nisht geblibn mer dortn.

399
00:23:53,762 --> 00:23:59,021
un, tsurik keyn Budapest, un vi lang zent ir gevezn in Budapest?

400
00:24:00,175 --> 00:24:05,740
kh'hob gearbet nokh a mol a por monat, un nokh dem, ikh hob ayngeshribn in a transport

401
00:24:05,740 --> 00:24:06,834
oyf YISRAEL.

402
00:24:07,080 --> 00:24:11,410
 ver hot aykh gezogt, v- ver hot mit aykh geredt...?

403
00:24:07,465 --> 00:24:08,843
nu, ⟨un mayn⟩...

404
00:24:09,830 --> 00:24:13,620
 mayn harts, mayn harts hot getsoygn oyf YISRAEL.

405
00:24:11,970 --> 00:24:14,124
a. aha.

406
00:24:14,063 --> 00:24:17,364
KEN. ikh hob nor gevolt YISRAEL, YISRAEL.

407
00:24:17,877 --> 00:24:23,507
un, ikh hob ayngeshribn. ze'mir geforn in a transport, nisht ikh aleyn.

408
00:24:23,850 --> 00:24:25,740
veyst vos s'heyst transport?

409
00:24:25,858 --> 00:24:30,695
a sakh, BAKHUROT, BAKHURIM zenen geven ayngeshribn.

410
00:24:30,904 --> 00:24:32,282
m'iz geforn.

411
00:24:32,187 --> 00:24:32,755
vu?

412
00:24:33,688 --> 00:24:39,504
koydem gegangen fun Budapest oyf OSTRIYA, BAREGEL, nokh a mol BAREGEL,

413
00:24:39,645 --> 00:24:42,018
⟨tsu fu- in OS-⟩ yo.

414
00:24:40,438 --> 00:24:43,300
yo? vi lang hot men gegangen?

415
00:24:43,729 --> 00:24:52,390
⟨⟩, ikh veys, a tog, a nakht. nisht, a por monat azoy vi oyf, Daytshnland, ⟨⟩, veynik.

416
00:24:52,774 --> 00:24:55,097
un s'iz geven KAYITS, sheyn.

417
00:24:56,807 --> 00:25:02,530
ze'mir gezesn bay nakht in droysn, un s'iz geven a, di levone hot gebrent...

418
00:25:03,220 --> 00:25:06,030
du veyst s'heyst HALEVANA? di levone.

419
00:25:06,030 --> 00:25:08,600
un a daytsh iz tsugekumen, hot er gezogt,

420
00:25:08,600 --> 00:25:14,722
"geyt nisht! zitst do, vart, vayl di RUSIM..." di RUS- RUSYA iz dortn geven, in,

421
00:25:15,133 --> 00:25:18,181
in OSTRALYA, in Est- OSTRIYA.

422
00:25:18,525 --> 00:25:22,569
un zey hobn UNK undz ho'mir gehert taken az zey zingen dortn RUSIT.

423
00:25:22,744 --> 00:25:32,368
zol'mir nisht geyn, vayl zey veln undz pakn un zey veln undz arestirn. dervayl zol'mir nisht geyn, zol'mir vartn biz ven di RUSIM geyen avek, un demls zol'mir geyn makhn LEHAMSHIKH vayter.

424
00:25:32,368 --> 00:25:33,990
un azoy ho'mir gemakht.

425
00:25:33,375 --> 00:25:36,400
 un vu zent ir gegangen?

426
00:25:34,080 --> 00:25:35,080
KEN.

427
00:25:36,396 --> 00:25:40,119
nu, zog ikh, ze'mir gegangen biz, OSTRIYA.

428
00:25:40,513 --> 00:25:42,852
biz OSTRIYA ze'mir gegangen.

429
00:25:42,927 --> 00:25:50,440
in OSTRIYA hot men undz ⟨oy-⟩ geleygt in RAKEVETn biz, TROFAIACH. TROFAIACH.

430
00:25:50,520 --> 00:25:54,294
ze'mir nisht gegangen BAREGEL biz TROFAIACH, nor azoy di GVUL ariber.

431
00:25:54,452 --> 00:25:56,488
un dortn in TROFAIACH,

432
00:25:57,523 --> 00:26:00,807
 hot men undz gefirt nokh dem oyf ITALYA,

433
00:26:01,422 --> 00:26:03,525
fun OSTRIYA oyf ITALYA.

434
00:26:04,628 --> 00:26:06,714
vu ahin in ITALYA?

435
00:26:06,703 --> 00:26:09,329
a! in a kibuts, dort vu kh'hob bakant mayn man.

436
00:26:09,235 --> 00:26:12,670
 vi hot geheysn der kibuts?

437
00:26:12,222 --> 00:26:16,294
 Borokhov, kibuts Borokhov, BECASTEL GANDOLFO,

438
00:26:16,294 --> 00:26:20,011
AL YA- lebn ROMA. dos iz geven lebn ROMA, KEN.

439
00:26:20,203 --> 00:26:24,297
un ir gedenkt, velkhe yor zent ir dort gekumen?

440
00:26:25,047 --> 00:26:26,537
in velekhe yor?

441
00:26:26,537 --> 00:26:29,228
in finef u- nokh di, bald,

442
00:26:29,228 --> 00:26:32,803
nokh di SHIKHRUR UNK fun di daytshn.

443
00:26:32,960 --> 00:26:35,993
 un vos hot men gemakht dortn in kibuts?

444
00:26:36,589 --> 00:26:42,320
m'hot gearbet. m'hot nisht gegebn BE- OKHEL BEKH⟨U⟩NAM. m'hot gearbet far UNRRA.

445
00:26:42,360 --> 00:26:44,548
mit ney-mashinen iz geven,

446
00:26:44,588 --> 00:26:46,070
un m'hot gearbet.

447
00:26:46,070 --> 00:26:50,909
ikh gedenk nisht vos m'hot geneyt, epes farshidene zakhn m'hot gearbet far UNRRA.

448
00:26:51,304 --> 00:26:54,656
di UNRRA mit Dzhoynt hot gegebn

449
00:26:54,915 --> 00:26:58,220
shtitsung tsu haltn di kibutsim.

450
00:26:59,556 --> 00:27:02,060
di kibutsim fun vu hobn gehat gelt?

451
00:27:02,374 --> 00:27:07,245
di UNRRA hot undz gegebn gelt, un azoy m'hot gelebt dortn.

452
00:27:07,521 --> 00:27:10,770
KEN. s'iz geven, m'hot gemakht a lebn.

453
00:27:11,098 --> 00:27:13,302
ITALYA iz geven zeyer sheyn.

454
00:27:14,136 --> 00:27:17,180
dortn m'hot gegesn a sakh, MAKARONIM.

455
00:27:17,180 --> 00:27:21,791
m'iz nor gek- ariber di grenets, m'hot shoyn ge- nor MAKARONIM, MAKARONIM.

456
00:27:22,303 --> 00:27:30,127
mayne groyse tokhter, oykh nor MAKARONIM hot zi gevolt esn, mit, ⟨P-⟩, PASTASCIUTTA mit MITS AGVANIYOT oyvn, mit gele kez.

457
00:27:29,323 --> 00:27:33,809
yo, un dertseyl undz, vi hot ir, gekant ayere man?

458
00:27:34,437 --> 00:27:38,160
nu, mayn, zayn bruder iz geven in dem kibuts.

459
00:27:38,554 --> 00:27:41,361
vi ikh bin gekumen in dem kibuts,

460
00:27:41,361 --> 00:27:45,129
⟨iz⟩ geven zayn bruder gekum- iz d- geven dortn shoyn,

461
00:27:45,355 --> 00:27:46,530
un mayn

462
00:27:47,363 --> 00:27:49,162
bru- mayn man

463
00:27:49,776 --> 00:27:52,217
⟨iz⟩ gekumen ale mol zen dem bruder.

464
00:27:52,749 --> 00:27:53,749
TODA.

